snippet.title: Crazy Candydish Trailer 5. #puzzlegame
snippet.description:
Mike is a game developer from New Jersey. He loves retro games and would love to discuss them with everyone. 

Please Subscribe.

Join us on Discord and suggest my next review!
https://discord.com/channels/1086828809334030438/1086828809883500556


Also, we have a website. http://www.x-raygames.com
You can buy some of the games I've made there. Also, there is a link to my Etsy store that sells arts and crafts.

I'm releasing my first game on Steam on March 30th. It's called Crazy Candydish:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2711550/Crazy_Candydish/

Join us on Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=113710295


We also have an Ambient Sound channel to help you get to sleep. You can Subscribe here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFiTPsu1pxmNPsnt2IovT0g?view_as=subscriber?sub_confirmation=1
